line_1: Come creeping from their secret Holes.
line_2: You'd joy to see the pretty Souls,

line_1: Come creeping from their secret Holes.
line_2: With wadling Steps and frowzy Poles,

line_1: Peeping in all the Chinks and Holes.
line_2: Then gastly round the Room she rowls

line_1: Of blinking Error to their secret holes,
line_2: Shall brighten Nature's face, shall drive the Moles
